WEBVTT

00:00:00.960 --> 00:00:06.080
you know I lean into empathy and humility and so I'd say always assume you're not the smartest in

00:00:06.080 --> 00:00:13.280
the room, ask a lot of questions and then be willing to adjust. I think as a leader I have

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:19.120
found more and more often I'm surrounded by diverse perspectives and understanding and what I

00:00:19.120 --> 00:00:23.920
might start the team down or you know shift the team around is usually not where we're going to

00:00:24.799 --> 00:00:29.440
and so I think it's great when you can step back, let other people lead you

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:33.680
and then you can evolve your perspective as a leader as well.

